OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FKen Bruce to leave BBC     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FRadio 2 show after 31 years
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BBC Radio 2's Ken Bruce has announced  
OL,6, on air that he is leaving the station  
OL,7, after 31 years hosting its weekday     
OL,8, mid-morning show.                      
OL,10,FHis slot is the most listened-to show  
OL,11,Fon British radio, and he will now join 
OL,12,Frival station Greatest Hits Radio.     
OL,14,F"I have decided the time is right for  
OL,15,Fme to move on from Radio 2," he said,  
OL,16,Fadding he'd had "a tremendously happy  
OL,17,Ftime" but it was "time for a change".  
OL,19,FHis departure comes after Steve Wright 
OL,20,Fleft after 23 years as afternoon host. 
